articles.author: David Lawder, Andrea Shalal
articles.description: Indonesia has agreed to eliminate tariffs on more than 99% of U.S. goods and scrap all non-tariff barriers facing American firms, while the U.S. will drop threatened tariffs on Indonesian products to 19% from 32%, the two countries said on Tuesday.
articles.title: Indonesia to cut tariffs, non-tariff barriers in US trade deal, Trump official says
